data.name: lblAboutUs.Text
data.value:
The Ballito lifestyle estate offers the best of coastal living.
The estate is set in the picturesque town of Ballito only 20 minutes from King Shaka International Airport.
Apartments are Wi-Fi ready and include free eco-friendly appliances.
The Ballito Hills 6-Star Green Rated Lifestyle Centre offers residents access to fantastic facilities within
beautifully landscaped surroundings.
